WEBVTT

01:43.030 --> 01:45.950
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.110 --> 01:49.050
[Episode 28]

01:51.990 --> 01:52.509
Qin.

02:15.670 --> 02:17.230
Why's the psychologist here?

02:17.950 --> 02:18.470
She's been here

02:18.470 --> 02:19.140
all these nights.

02:19.190 --> 02:19.970
Didn't you see?

02:21.079 --> 02:22.110
I was so busy that

02:22.130 --> 02:23.050
I didn't notice.

02:24.290 --> 02:25.240
What's she doing?

02:26.070 --> 02:26.900
I don't know.

02:26.950 --> 02:27.910
I think she's been watching movies.

02:28.470 --> 02:29.440
Movies?

02:29.910 --> 02:31.060
Watching movies here?

02:31.390 --> 02:32.240
Should she be going

02:32.270 --> 02:33.230
to the theater with you?

02:33.430 --> 02:34.110
It's with you.

02:51.930 --> 02:53.620
[Ninghai Runying]

02:55.920 --> 02:58.130
[Ninghai Runying Pictures Co., Ltd.]

03:14.930 --> 03:15.730
Sleep in bed No. 6.

03:22.170 --> 03:23.079
What are you looking at?

03:23.360 --> 03:24.440
Never seen a man before?

03:40.140 --> 03:40.960
Hey! You are...

03:41.430 --> 03:42.770
Y-You're that...

03:43.110 --> 03:44.680
superstar Yu Bofeng, yeah?

03:45.190 --> 03:45.920
You're so handsome.

03:45.950 --> 03:47.380
No wonder you're a star.

03:47.829 --> 03:48.680
I know about you.

03:48.710 --> 03:49.890
You hit a cop, right?

03:50.030 --> 03:50.790
Everyone's talking

03:50.790 --> 03:51.340
about it.

03:51.790 --> 03:52.820
I support you.

03:52.990 --> 03:53.950
Can I take a photo with you

03:54.030 --> 03:54.590
after we get out?

03:56.150 --> 03:56.800
How about this?

03:57.540 --> 03:58.590
After I'm released,

03:58.670 --> 03:59.510
if you want to

03:59.510 --> 04:00.340
handle that cop,

04:00.430 --> 04:00.910
I'll help you.

04:03.390 --> 04:04.040
I'll help you.

04:06.260 --> 04:06.910
You'll help me?

04:07.910 --> 04:08.870
I can fight.

04:08.890 --> 04:09.750
I'm in here because

04:09.750 --> 04:10.350
of assault.

04:10.510 --> 04:12.270
Outside, I-I have many

04:12.430 --> 04:13.150
buddies.

04:13.590 --> 04:13.950
You...

04:14.400 --> 04:15.670
You're a celebrity after all.

04:15.710 --> 04:16.660
Let me join you.

04:16.829 --> 04:17.940
Then I can brag to my friends

04:18.029 --> 04:18.899
outside.

04:18.950 --> 04:19.550
Let me brag.

04:22.070 --> 04:23.150
I want to kill someone.

04:25.310 --> 04:25.910
Kill?

04:28.150 --> 04:28.870
Are you crazy?

04:30.750 --> 04:32.150
K-Kill someone?

05:06.430 --> 05:07.230
You know...

05:07.270 --> 05:08.600
Hey. Don't move.

05:08.420 --> 05:09.850
♫As the city flickers♫

05:08.710 --> 05:09.600
It'll burn you.

05:10.510 --> 05:11.230
You know...

05:11.130 --> 05:13.980
♫It's as gentle as wind wrapping around rain♫

05:13.190 --> 05:15.310
It's been so many years.

05:15.200 --> 05:16.490
♫And you, who love to smile♫

05:16.750 --> 05:17.990
Why's Yu Bofeng suddenly

05:17.510 --> 05:19.960
♫Always offer your happiness to me first♫

05:18.010 --> 05:19.690
unable to accept it?

05:20.990 --> 05:23.330
♫The humor of time♫

05:21.940 --> 05:22.840
Someone must have

05:22.870 --> 05:24.430
provoked him.

05:24.820 --> 05:27.270
♫No one to blame for breaking the promise♫

05:25.190 --> 05:26.550
But it's been a long time.

05:26.550 --> 05:28.590
No matter how he was provoked, would he...

05:28.340 --> 05:34.100
♫It's because we met too soon that we missed each other♫

05:29.980 --> 05:30.900
Besides,

05:31.230 --> 05:33.510
Yu Zheng and I were involved in that.

05:34.070 --> 05:35.110
Who told him?

05:35.480 --> 05:37.100
♫We're stranded at sunset♫

05:36.750 --> 05:37.680
I don't understand.

05:38.210 --> 05:41.070
♫My sunburnt face doesn't mean a word♫

05:38.960 --> 05:40.590
Then don't think about it.

05:41.460 --> 05:42.440
Isn't your colleague

05:42.360 --> 05:43.790
♫The stubborn me♫

05:42.470 --> 05:43.560
keeping an eye on it?

05:44.760 --> 05:46.300
Rest a few days, okay?

05:45.020 --> 05:47.710
♫I always think of the far future♫

05:46.430 --> 05:47.430
Stop thinking about it, okay?

05:48.500 --> 05:50.570
♫I walk willfully♫

05:51.940 --> 05:54.860
♫Like a star revolving around♫

05:54.480 --> 05:56.090
Does this really work?

05:55.500 --> 05:56.820
♫I turn around♫

05:56.110 --> 05:57.820
I still don't feel anything.

05:57.980 --> 06:01.480
♫But you're not behind me♫

05:58.480 --> 05:59.320
Moxibustion

05:59.350 --> 06:00.600
takes time to take effect.

06:00.630 --> 06:01.790
It won't heal you instantly.

06:02.470 --> 06:03.150
I'll do it for you

06:03.150 --> 06:04.730
♫Losing you♫

06:03.190 --> 06:04.110
every night.

06:04.590 --> 06:05.590
It's good for your health.

06:05.550 --> 06:07.730
♫It's so unreal♫

06:06.990 --> 06:07.910
You're such

06:08.030 --> 06:09.840
an experienced anesthesiologist.

06:08.920 --> 06:10.350
♫I hurt my love♫

06:09.870 --> 06:11.170
Don't you have...

06:11.060 --> 06:12.010
♫But still hope to♫

06:11.820 --> 06:13.320
Don't you have an injection

06:12.760 --> 06:15.450
♫Start anew♫

06:13.350 --> 06:15.460
that can take away

06:15.510 --> 06:17.230
all my pain instantly?

06:16.650 --> 06:18.670
♫There’s a certain kind of squander♫

06:17.800 --> 06:18.510
Yes.

06:18.750 --> 06:20.550
We happen to have that.

06:19.610 --> 06:21.740
♫Where I'm late to know who loves me♫

06:21.030 --> 06:21.630
Muscle relaxants.

06:22.550 --> 06:23.720
What happens after that?

06:23.300 --> 06:25.270
♫When you're not here♫

06:23.870 --> 06:24.630
After that,

06:24.750 --> 06:26.390
you won't feel it even if I pinch you.

06:26.070 --> 06:29.380
♫Life becomes aimless♫

06:26.590 --> 06:27.400
What? Totally...

06:27.430 --> 06:28.160
totally relaxed?

06:28.190 --> 06:29.080
Yeah, not a part

06:29.110 --> 06:30.150
of your body will be tense.

06:30.240 --> 06:31.910
♫I miss you♫

06:33.000 --> 06:35.140
♫It's so real♫

06:33.800 --> 06:34.590
Do you want it?

06:34.830 --> 06:35.640
I'll inject you.

06:35.860 --> 06:36.700
Forget it.

06:36.230 --> 06:37.780
♫The person I trust♫

06:36.950 --> 06:38.450
Better me than a stranger.

06:38.340 --> 06:39.460
♫Insists on separating♫

06:39.970 --> 06:42.900
♫Who can explain?♫

06:44.130 --> 06:46.050
♫I'm not afraid of your happiness♫

07:00.170 --> 07:00.960
Dad.

07:01.530 --> 07:02.370
Chengyi.

07:02.670 --> 07:03.950
Come have tea with me.

07:05.510 --> 07:07.140
Is... What's the matter?

07:07.590 --> 07:08.320
Nothing.

07:08.670 --> 07:09.720
Just to have a chat.

07:10.390 --> 07:10.900
Okay.

07:11.230 --> 07:11.720
Okay.

07:11.750 --> 07:12.390
I'll...

07:12.880 --> 07:13.870
go over later.

07:15.180 --> 07:15.720
Okay.

07:40.710 --> 07:41.420
Dad.

07:52.630 --> 07:54.610
I ran into Director Xing.

07:55.430 --> 07:57.240
Why didn't you tell me about

07:57.270 --> 07:58.550
something so huge?

07:59.230 --> 08:01.020
It happened when I just joined the police force.

08:02.150 --> 08:04.470
Although so many years have passed,

08:05.560 --> 08:06.630
I still haven't

08:06.670 --> 08:07.920
moved past it.

08:09.500 --> 08:11.040
That Yu Bofeng

08:11.520 --> 08:12.750
doing such a thing

08:13.720 --> 08:15.020
even now...

08:16.230 --> 08:17.290
To be honest,

08:18.370 --> 08:19.210
I understand him.

08:21.870 --> 08:22.840
You can?

08:25.850 --> 08:26.880
By then,

08:27.230 --> 08:28.670
no one will understand you.

08:29.910 --> 08:31.350
You can't be soft-hearted

08:31.380 --> 08:32.179
about this.

08:37.490 --> 08:39.059
I did something similar

08:39.309 --> 08:40.909
when I was younger too.

08:42.360 --> 08:43.580
In your first year of high school,

08:44.230 --> 08:45.270
I caught a kid;

08:46.350 --> 08:46.950
16 years old.

08:48.870 --> 08:49.600
After middle school,

08:49.630 --> 08:50.710
he began working at a factory.

08:51.590 --> 08:52.360
One day,

08:52.390 --> 08:54.390
he had a dispute with the foreman

08:54.910 --> 08:55.430
and hit him.

08:55.670 --> 08:56.890
He's a big kid.

08:56.950 --> 08:58.470
His punches caused

08:58.990 --> 08:59.750
serious injury.

09:01.080 --> 09:04.040
He should've been indicted

09:04.710 --> 09:05.770
for assault.

09:07.100 --> 09:08.210
After I detained him,

09:08.470 --> 09:10.470
he was very apologetic.

09:12.280 --> 09:13.100
He looked

09:13.150 --> 09:14.410
to be around your age

09:14.630 --> 09:15.670
and was obedient.

09:17.590 --> 09:18.510
So I got soft-hearted.

09:19.430 --> 09:20.670
I went to his parents

09:21.270 --> 09:23.430
and suggested paying compensation

09:24.690 --> 09:26.150
to try to get a lighter sentence.

09:26.320 --> 09:27.670
His parents told me

09:27.800 --> 09:28.470
they have no money

09:29.870 --> 09:31.010
and we can deal with him

09:31.310 --> 09:31.870
however.

09:31.920 --> 09:32.520
My goodness.

09:33.280 --> 09:33.870
So

09:33.890 --> 09:35.140
I went to persuade

09:35.170 --> 09:36.070
the victim

09:36.230 --> 09:37.680
and got a letter of forgiveness.

09:38.030 --> 09:38.910
I even personally

09:39.310 --> 09:40.010
vouched for him

09:40.550 --> 09:41.960
and applied for a lighter sentence

09:42.090 --> 09:43.070
to the court.

09:44.140 --> 09:45.010
Back then,

09:45.310 --> 09:46.150
our former captain

09:46.530 --> 09:48.060
told me to stay out of it.

09:48.590 --> 09:49.220
He said that

09:49.250 --> 09:50.580
if that kid violated the law

09:50.610 --> 09:51.530
again,

09:51.590 --> 09:53.050
everything I was doing

09:53.070 --> 09:54.170
would be in vain.

09:54.680 --> 09:55.880
I chose not to believe it.

09:57.730 --> 09:58.480
In the end,

09:59.790 --> 10:01.240
he was imprisoned for two years.

10:01.370 --> 10:02.250
When he came out,

10:02.270 --> 10:03.270
he was 18.

10:04.560 --> 10:05.550
He was so young

10:05.670 --> 10:07.150
with such a long way to go

10:07.170 --> 10:08.220
in the future.

10:08.500 --> 10:09.530
So I quickly

10:09.560 --> 10:11.390
asked around to get him a job

10:11.740 --> 10:13.110
so that he can integrate

10:13.140 --> 10:14.350
into the society soon.

10:18.170 --> 10:19.260
But not long after,

10:20.140 --> 10:20.780
he killed someone.

10:21.470 --> 10:24.240
The reason for the murder

10:24.270 --> 10:25.360
was very simple.

10:25.600 --> 10:26.710
It was because

10:26.790 --> 10:28.430
of some minor arguments.

10:30.030 --> 10:30.950
This time, my former captain

10:30.990 --> 10:31.590
didn't let me go.

10:33.600 --> 10:35.350
After my colleague detained him,

10:35.360 --> 10:36.520
he told me that

10:37.750 --> 10:38.980
that kid

10:39.670 --> 10:41.370
was so apologetic.

10:41.400 --> 10:42.080
He thought

10:42.110 --> 10:43.000
he'd meet another

10:43.150 --> 10:44.960
soft-hearted person like me

10:45.070 --> 10:46.270
who'd help him suppress it.

10:51.000 --> 10:53.550
When I wanted to join the police academy,

10:53.830 --> 10:54.870
you were very supportive.

10:56.080 --> 10:57.610
Then you suddenly changed your mind,

10:58.150 --> 11:00.260
insisting that I go to a regular school.

11:01.550 --> 11:02.710
Is it also related to this?

11:05.370 --> 11:06.190
Yes.

11:07.440 --> 11:08.570
I was worried

11:09.080 --> 11:11.190
you'd encounter what you're going through now.

11:13.550 --> 11:14.450
You know,

11:14.790 --> 11:16.230
if you want to be a good cop,

11:16.710 --> 11:18.630
you have to be really tough

11:18.830 --> 11:20.200
mentally.

11:23.310 --> 11:24.800
Do you regret helping him?

11:26.900 --> 11:28.820
I regret being

11:28.870 --> 11:30.270
so self-righteous.

11:32.990 --> 11:33.670
That kid

11:34.030 --> 11:36.800
receiving his due punishment

11:36.830 --> 11:38.690
was the right way to help him

11:38.870 --> 11:39.870
and protect him.

11:43.830 --> 11:44.470
Son.

11:45.510 --> 11:47.030
Since you've chosen

11:47.050 --> 11:47.980
this path,

11:48.670 --> 11:49.830
you must stick to

11:49.870 --> 11:50.830
your principles.

11:51.510 --> 11:52.720
Step by step,

11:52.750 --> 11:54.040
advance honestly.

11:54.680 --> 11:55.680
Failure to protect others

11:55.900 --> 11:57.150
and excessive bias

11:58.700 --> 11:59.980
are all taboos.

12:00.680 --> 12:01.390
Remember this.

12:03.140 --> 12:03.930
Understood.

12:04.560 --> 12:05.620
Really?

12:06.030 --> 12:06.470
Yes.

12:17.290 --> 12:18.130
Jiang.

12:19.180 --> 12:20.190
Jiang!

12:20.590 --> 12:21.800
Wrong door.

12:22.190 --> 12:22.960
He's injured

12:22.990 --> 12:23.750
and resting at home.

12:24.600 --> 12:25.480
Jiang!

12:28.230 --> 12:29.340
Jiang!

12:31.290 --> 12:32.110
-Jiang!
-Stop ringing.

12:32.170 --> 12:32.850
What's up?

12:33.790 --> 12:34.450
Where'd you go?

12:34.540 --> 12:35.760
I just came up.

12:35.990 --> 12:37.110
Is your back okay?

12:37.160 --> 12:38.050
Almost.

12:38.940 --> 12:39.890
Why are you two here?

12:39.920 --> 12:41.160
We have something to discuss with you.

12:44.030 --> 12:45.540
We looked into Mr. Ke.

12:45.620 --> 12:46.490
He's not even

12:46.570 --> 12:47.390
in our field.

12:47.550 --> 12:48.860
We also heard that he was

12:48.910 --> 12:49.760
imprisoned

12:49.790 --> 12:50.990
for six years for fraud.

12:51.750 --> 12:53.030
There must be something off.

12:53.670 --> 12:54.510
Jiang.

12:54.630 --> 12:56.830
Tell me. What should I do?

12:58.100 --> 12:59.260
Reviewing this contract

12:59.830 --> 13:01.030
isn't within my capabilities.

13:01.050 --> 13:02.800
Get a commercial lawyer

13:02.830 --> 13:03.510
to help you.

13:04.110 --> 13:04.990
I did.

13:05.530 --> 13:07.260
They said as per the contract,

13:07.390 --> 13:08.190
there's no way out.

13:08.390 --> 13:09.290
No way out?

13:13.390 --> 13:14.230
Well then,

13:14.420 --> 13:15.430
it'd be tough

13:15.750 --> 13:17.410
to dispute this contract

13:18.270 --> 13:19.080
legally.

13:19.200 --> 13:20.280
Wait, c-can I

13:20.310 --> 13:21.130
sue Mr. Ke

13:21.150 --> 13:22.580
for fraud?

13:22.600 --> 13:24.090
How will you sue him?

13:25.350 --> 13:26.570
Because he has a criminal record?

13:26.810 --> 13:28.720
You signed this contract voluntarily, right?

13:29.720 --> 13:31.650
You signed it and stamped your fingerprint

13:31.670 --> 13:32.990
after reading it, right?

13:34.300 --> 13:35.490
So how's it fraud?

13:35.680 --> 13:36.900
You signed it yourself.

13:37.260 --> 13:37.860
Then...

13:38.220 --> 13:38.980
What should we do?

13:39.000 --> 13:40.070
Just leave it be?

13:40.150 --> 13:40.920
We're trapped

13:40.950 --> 13:42.040
by this project.

13:42.680 --> 13:43.630
Zhong.

13:43.670 --> 13:44.160
You've

13:44.190 --> 13:45.300
never once suffered a loss,

13:45.320 --> 13:47.000
so you've always been careless.

13:47.240 --> 13:48.070
A contract stipulates

13:48.150 --> 13:50.190
restrictive conditions on both parties'

13:50.270 --> 13:51.040
actions.

13:51.220 --> 13:52.560
And what's written in this?

13:52.910 --> 13:54.110
You're giving him money

13:54.130 --> 13:55.180
but he's restricting you.

13:55.390 --> 13:56.710
No restrictions against him.

13:57.660 --> 13:58.530
And you transferred

13:58.560 --> 14:00.240
all the money in one go.

14:00.430 --> 14:01.280
How'll you get it back?

14:05.690 --> 14:07.770
Then... Then what should I do?

14:08.620 --> 14:10.290
With this matter...

14:12.000 --> 14:14.750
I think you can only discuss this with them.

14:15.070 --> 14:16.430
Do your accounts

14:16.630 --> 14:18.090
and see what's your limit.

14:18.690 --> 14:20.940
Just try to minimize losses.

14:21.710 --> 14:22.680
Discuss with whom?

14:22.840 --> 14:23.840
Wen Peng?

14:23.880 --> 14:25.060
Him?

14:25.410 --> 14:26.650
He gave us all sorts of excuses.

14:26.680 --> 14:27.610
Wen Peng said

14:27.650 --> 14:29.060
even if we withdraw now,

14:29.080 --> 14:30.230
we won't get a penny.

14:31.820 --> 14:33.050
It's my fault for trusting him

14:33.120 --> 14:34.070
back then.

14:34.110 --> 14:35.910
Since we're old friends,

14:36.090 --> 14:37.230
I just got Dalu to skim through it

14:37.270 --> 14:38.130
and signed it.

14:38.880 --> 14:39.320
Now,

14:39.350 --> 14:40.670
what I don't understand the most

14:40.690 --> 14:41.190
is that

14:41.370 --> 14:43.600
shouldn't Wen Peng have run a background check

14:43.930 --> 14:44.920
on Mr. Ke

14:44.950 --> 14:46.870
before cooperating with him?

14:47.130 --> 14:49.090
Even I could find out his criminal record.

14:49.430 --> 14:50.810
There's no way Wen Peng couldn't.

14:50.840 --> 14:52.020
Well, his criminal record

14:52.110 --> 14:52.650
doesn't affect

14:52.680 --> 14:53.840
their cooperation.

14:53.870 --> 14:54.310
But...

14:55.430 --> 14:56.500
I now suspect

14:56.550 --> 14:57.680
they're in cahoots!

14:58.070 --> 14:59.900
What does Wen Peng get from this?

15:00.050 --> 15:01.760
He invested money in it too.

15:02.430 --> 15:04.030
To suffer losses with me?

15:04.630 --> 15:05.720
What for?

15:07.230 --> 15:09.230
Read the contract carefully.

15:09.320 --> 15:11.270
You invested your money

15:11.600 --> 15:13.590
into their project.

15:13.730 --> 15:15.050
How he'll use the money

15:15.060 --> 15:16.120
is up to him.

15:16.380 --> 15:17.470
You have no say.

15:21.990 --> 15:22.830
When did you start

15:22.830 --> 15:23.550
working with him?

15:24.530 --> 15:25.410
It was...

15:28.130 --> 15:30.210
On the day you made up with Lu Yan.

15:30.700 --> 15:31.980
Weren't we having hotpot?

15:32.160 --> 15:33.090
I went to his office

15:33.110 --> 15:33.670
in the afternoon

15:33.900 --> 15:35.780
with two bottles of good wine.

15:35.910 --> 15:37.100
I told him

15:37.130 --> 15:39.040
you made up with Lu Yan

15:39.120 --> 15:40.450
and Tang Jie's pregnant.

15:41.120 --> 15:42.280
So I asked if I could

15:42.310 --> 15:43.970
get some shares of that project

15:44.230 --> 15:45.350
to make some diaper money.

15:47.120 --> 15:47.940
Zhong.

15:48.890 --> 15:50.370
I don't know what to say.

15:51.570 --> 15:52.700
We're buddies.

15:53.480 --> 15:54.350
We go way back,

15:54.370 --> 15:55.140
right?

15:55.340 --> 15:55.860
Yeah.

15:56.160 --> 15:57.320
After all these years,

15:57.350 --> 15:57.870
you should

15:57.910 --> 15:58.870
understand things more or less.

15:59.730 --> 16:00.900
You even asked for a cooperation

16:00.920 --> 16:02.010
after bragging to him

16:02.320 --> 16:03.330
about me and Lu Yan?

16:08.120 --> 16:08.670
Wait.

16:08.690 --> 16:11.000
You mean he did it on purpose?

16:11.440 --> 16:12.600
I don't know about that.

16:16.330 --> 16:17.050
I just...

16:17.080 --> 16:18.150
I-I was so happy

16:18.180 --> 16:18.900
that I just

16:18.930 --> 16:20.030
let it slip!

16:20.210 --> 16:21.350
T-Then...

16:21.500 --> 16:22.840
What should I do?

16:26.130 --> 16:27.300
I doubt there's a way out

16:27.320 --> 16:28.000
with

16:28.870 --> 16:29.620
this contract.

16:30.460 --> 16:31.890
Swallow your pride

16:32.590 --> 16:33.760
and discuss it with him.

16:34.510 --> 16:35.510
Try to minimize losses

16:35.530 --> 16:36.590
however you can.

16:36.790 --> 16:37.660
F-Fine.

16:38.180 --> 16:38.790
I can only

16:38.790 --> 16:39.840
take it a step at a time.

16:41.390 --> 16:43.230
Don’t tell Lu Yan about this.

16:43.760 --> 16:44.970
I’m worried she’d tell Tang Jie.

16:45.220 --> 16:46.670
Tang Jie's pregnant.

16:46.830 --> 16:48.060
I don’t want to worry her.

16:48.780 --> 16:49.810
Don't worry.

16:54.430 --> 16:56.050
If there's nothing you can do,

16:58.590 --> 16:59.390
try investigating

16:59.390 --> 17:00.150
their company.

17:06.060 --> 17:07.240
Right!

17:08.520 --> 17:09.260
Let's go, Dalu.

17:09.310 --> 17:10.099
Let's hurry.

17:10.400 --> 17:11.690
Thank you, Jiang.

17:11.980 --> 17:13.339
What'd we do without you?

17:17.920 --> 17:24.359
[Limin Detention Center]

17:23.849 --> 17:24.500
Hello.

17:24.640 --> 17:27.319
[Don't test the law; Break it and you'll be punished]

17:25.280 --> 17:25.980
I'm sorry.

17:26.010 --> 17:27.530
Yu Bofeng said he doesn't want to see you.

17:28.830 --> 17:29.740
Comrade.

17:32.840 --> 17:37.350
[Don't test the law; Break it and you'll be punished]

17:33.520 --> 17:35.210
Can I trouble you

17:35.240 --> 17:36.780
to give this to him?

17:43.760 --> 17:44.210
Sure.

17:44.230 --> 17:45.020
Thank you.

17:49.980 --> 17:58.080
[Anshan, Ninghai Public Security
Criminal Investigation Unit]

18:23.980 --> 18:24.640
Professor Yu.

18:27.230 --> 18:28.530
Why don't you go home and rest?

18:28.550 --> 18:29.950
You'll catch a cold if you sleep here.

18:31.830 --> 18:32.630
It's fine.

18:33.100 --> 18:34.560
I can't sleep anyway.

18:35.730 --> 18:37.160
I'll just finish this.

18:37.840 --> 18:39.300
I've always wanted to ask you

18:39.330 --> 18:40.180
what you're watching

18:40.180 --> 18:40.880
every day.

18:42.930 --> 18:43.900
Just this and that.

18:43.920 --> 18:45.360
You must be preparing

18:45.390 --> 18:46.620
for your classes?

19:30.600 --> 19:32.840
Shouldn't Wen Peng have run a background check

19:33.030 --> 19:34.150
on Mr. Ke

19:34.190 --> 19:36.290
before cooperating with him?

19:36.350 --> 19:37.540
I told him

19:37.570 --> 19:39.310
you made up with Lu Yan

19:39.720 --> 19:41.030
and Tang Jie's pregnant.

19:41.180 --> 19:43.020
Wen Peng got into a fight

19:43.850 --> 19:45.510
with a patient's family.

19:45.800 --> 19:47.480
He isn't usually so rash.

19:47.550 --> 19:49.640
His dad beat him up as a kid,

19:49.670 --> 19:51.240
and his mom didn't protect him.

19:51.380 --> 19:52.450
He may be traumatized

19:52.550 --> 19:53.270
in this aspect.

19:53.330 --> 19:54.630
When he saw that,

19:54.770 --> 19:56.340
he was reminded of his childhood.

19:56.360 --> 19:58.060
He was always beaten up as a kid?

20:17.670 --> 20:18.510
Here you are.

20:18.530 --> 20:19.150
You're back.

20:19.450 --> 20:20.110
Yeah, I'm back.

20:20.130 --> 20:21.190
Why are you so late?

20:21.220 --> 20:22.960
I had many operations.

20:22.980 --> 20:23.650
I just finished.

20:23.670 --> 20:24.790
Why are you sitting here?

20:25.350 --> 20:26.550
To get some fresh air.

20:26.950 --> 20:28.260
How's your back?

20:28.720 --> 20:29.950
I think I'm almost recovered.

20:29.970 --> 20:31.070
I'll go to work tomorrow.

20:31.090 --> 20:32.000
Tomorrow?

20:32.900 --> 20:34.480
Then let me sit with you.

20:42.920 --> 20:44.290
I saw...

20:44.530 --> 20:46.170
three cups in the living room.

20:46.200 --> 20:47.260
Did someone visit?

20:48.400 --> 20:49.640
Zhong and Dalu came

20:49.820 --> 20:51.120
to discuss something.

20:53.060 --> 20:54.120
About what?

20:54.640 --> 20:55.820
It's about their company.

20:57.760 --> 20:58.390
Alright.

21:02.890 --> 21:03.680
Lu Yan.

21:06.440 --> 21:07.730
What do you think...

21:08.860 --> 21:10.230
of Wen Peng?

21:11.220 --> 21:11.940
I...

21:13.220 --> 21:14.740
I don't really

21:15.280 --> 21:16.340
think about him.

21:20.600 --> 21:21.890
I've known him for so long,

21:21.950 --> 21:23.670
but I don't know him well.

21:24.440 --> 21:25.750
Didn't you say

21:25.830 --> 21:27.030
he was abused

21:27.550 --> 21:29.270
as a kid by his father?

21:30.130 --> 21:31.650
Is there anything else

21:31.950 --> 21:33.270
that we don't know?

21:35.430 --> 21:36.430
There's one.

21:37.350 --> 21:38.720
I heard it from Mr. Han.

21:38.910 --> 21:39.830
Didn't Wen Peng

21:39.850 --> 21:40.920
always do well

21:40.960 --> 21:42.440
in school?

21:42.580 --> 21:44.240
One day, he suddenly

21:44.390 --> 21:45.340
quit school

21:45.730 --> 21:46.780
to go abroad.

21:47.820 --> 21:48.960
He left without even collecting

21:48.990 --> 21:49.590
his diploma.

21:50.250 --> 21:51.870
Even his dad was unware

21:51.910 --> 21:53.670
and only found out when the school informed him.

21:55.190 --> 21:56.420
So he's always been

21:56.470 --> 21:58.110
unsociable since then?

21:58.630 --> 21:59.400
Apart from his dad,

21:59.430 --> 22:00.950
has he mentioned anyone from his family?

22:01.250 --> 22:02.490
I don't think so.

22:05.550 --> 22:06.330
Back then,

22:07.890 --> 22:08.880
I guess I'd never seen him

22:08.920 --> 22:10.290
having close friends either.

22:13.580 --> 22:14.670
Then...

22:16.130 --> 22:18.320
with Deng Man...

22:19.210 --> 22:20.980
that is, was he close

22:21.580 --> 22:22.900
to you girls?

22:24.080 --> 22:25.780
I doubt Man knows him.

22:26.060 --> 22:27.660
As for Ding Jing...

22:28.600 --> 22:29.240
I don't know.

22:34.990 --> 22:35.980
What's wrong?

22:36.770 --> 22:37.370
Nothing.

22:38.960 --> 22:40.540
I just think we've never

22:41.300 --> 22:42.650
really known him.

22:55.360 --> 22:55.870
Hello?

22:55.920 --> 22:56.960
Hello, where are you?

22:56.990 --> 22:58.110
We have important leads.

22:58.190 --> 22:59.280
Come to the team now.

22:59.900 --> 23:00.660
Now?

23:01.130 --> 23:01.530
Okay.

23:04.000 --> 23:05.290
I need to go to the bureau.

23:05.960 --> 23:06.560
Now?

23:10.190 --> 23:11.760
Didn't you say tomorrow?

23:12.400 --> 23:13.320
Something came up.

23:13.560 --> 23:14.580
I'll be back soon.

23:14.780 --> 23:15.520
Let's go inside.

23:15.790 --> 23:16.360
Don't catch a cold.

23:17.590 --> 23:18.310
Let's go.

23:18.960 --> 23:20.650
Come on. Let's go in.

23:20.610 --> 23:22.630
[Anshan, Ninghai Public Security
Criminal Investigation Unit]

23:32.320 --> 23:33.390
Is this...

23:34.400 --> 23:35.200
Li Ruonan?

23:35.790 --> 23:36.440
Yes.

23:40.570 --> 23:41.170
Fast forward

23:41.200 --> 23:42.670
to the

23:42.950 --> 23:44.040
end credits.

23:46.310 --> 23:47.500
[Love On a Sunny Day]

23:47.500 --> 23:49.290
[Producer: Ninghai Runying Pictures Co., Ltd.]

23:49.290 --> 23:50.530
[Actors]

23:50.550 --> 23:50.690
[Guest Stars]

23:52.830 --> 23:53.670
Dubbing,

23:53.960 --> 23:55.810
actors, screenwriters,

23:56.300 --> 23:59.270
Art Design, Post-production, Props...

23:58.130 --> 23:58.680
[Post-production team]

23:58.680 --> 23:59.560
[Props team]

23:59.560 --> 24:03.480
[Action team]

24:00.230 --> 24:00.760
Action—

24:00.790 --> 24:01.120
Stop!

24:04.150 --> 24:04.980
Liu Lin.

24:05.190 --> 24:06.030
Zhang Xueqiang.

24:06.050 --> 24:06.950
Chen Kaimin.

24:07.070 --> 24:07.870
Zhang Limin.

24:07.870 --> 24:08.780
Xiao Wei.

24:08.810 --> 24:09.970
Zhang Jiaqi.

24:11.210 --> 24:12.050
Xiao Wei

24:12.100 --> 24:13.910
should be Li Ruonan's pseudonym.

24:14.720 --> 24:15.720
Pseudonym...

24:16.320 --> 24:17.200
No wonder

24:17.230 --> 24:18.030
we couldn't find her

24:18.050 --> 24:18.760
in the credits.

24:20.040 --> 24:20.940
Keep playing it.

24:22.000 --> 24:23.570
[Ninghai Runying Pictures Co., Ltd.]

24:23.910 --> 24:24.890
Wen Peng's company?

24:28.410 --> 24:29.210
Qin Yue.

24:30.250 --> 24:32.020
Go check up on

24:32.050 --> 24:33.250
martial arts director...

24:33.570 --> 24:34.760
What’s his name... Liu Lin.

24:34.780 --> 24:35.750
Find out where he is.

24:35.770 --> 24:36.780
If you find him,

24:37.010 --> 24:37.850
ask him about

24:37.880 --> 24:38.660
Li Ruonan.

24:38.690 --> 24:39.340
Okay.

24:39.460 --> 24:40.100
Let's go.

24:40.120 --> 24:40.770
Hao,

24:40.800 --> 24:42.330
stay to help Jiang.

24:44.960 --> 24:46.310
How'd you figure out

24:46.350 --> 24:47.190
that Li Ruonan

24:47.230 --> 24:48.550
is linked to Wen Peng?

24:49.490 --> 24:51.400
Because of something Yu Bofeng said.

24:51.720 --> 24:53.740
You're all birds of a feather.

24:55.630 --> 24:57.200
You framed Aunt Wang back then.

24:57.240 --> 24:58.430
Would you let me go now?

24:58.450 --> 24:59.550
Through the mouths

24:59.580 --> 25:00.520
of the police,

25:00.580 --> 25:02.120
I can't even imagine

25:02.150 --> 25:04.180
what a deplorable villain I'd become.

25:04.900 --> 25:05.990
What do you mean?

25:06.010 --> 25:07.900
Didn't you say it yourself?

25:07.920 --> 25:09.890
Regardless if Aunt Wang was a thief or not,

25:11.040 --> 25:12.730
to protect yourselves,

25:13.040 --> 25:14.670
you'd classify her as one.

25:15.790 --> 25:17.470
After thinking about it,

25:17.630 --> 25:19.270
I'm sure I've never said that.

25:21.460 --> 25:23.390
So you mean...

25:23.410 --> 25:24.410
Wen Peng

25:24.650 --> 25:26.480
twisted your words?

25:26.740 --> 25:27.670
Think about it.

25:28.310 --> 25:29.690
As the head

25:29.750 --> 25:31.260
of a talent agency,

25:31.330 --> 25:32.990
he just wants me

25:33.070 --> 25:35.000
to stop seeing Yu Bofeng.

25:35.020 --> 25:36.710
But I've agreed to that.

25:36.860 --> 25:38.340
So why did he go one step further?

25:38.480 --> 25:39.740
Let's assume that Wen Peng

25:39.770 --> 25:41.120
is the mastermind.

25:41.640 --> 25:43.120
Then he must be in contact

25:43.170 --> 25:44.450
with Li Ruonan.

25:45.610 --> 25:47.130
Li Ruonan came to Ninghai City after

25:47.160 --> 25:48.540
graduating from martial arts school.

25:48.790 --> 25:49.900
It's most likely that

25:49.990 --> 25:51.950
she'd be a stunt double for films and series.

25:52.770 --> 25:53.400
If we could

25:53.430 --> 25:54.310
find Li Ruonan

25:54.330 --> 25:55.610
in Wen Peng's works,

25:56.000 --> 25:57.750
doesn't it prove that

25:57.760 --> 25:58.940
the two of them

25:59.130 --> 26:00.600
are more or less associated?

26:07.060 --> 26:08.610
Should we look for Wen Peng?

26:11.090 --> 26:12.260
It's not the time yet.

26:13.130 --> 26:13.940
Let's wait a bit more.

26:15.160 --> 26:15.970
Director, you see,

26:16.110 --> 26:17.020
we're here

26:17.050 --> 26:18.250
to ask you about something.

26:18.820 --> 26:19.850
Do you know her?

26:19.870 --> 26:21.140
I heard she was

26:21.190 --> 26:22.900
a stunt double in your film.

26:23.280 --> 26:24.360
I know her.

26:24.740 --> 26:25.820
She's Xiao Wei.

26:26.120 --> 26:26.860
Xiao Wei?

26:27.110 --> 26:28.190
Are you close?

26:28.230 --> 26:29.740
Not really.

26:29.770 --> 26:31.680
I just know her through work.

26:32.310 --> 26:33.630
How did you know each other?

26:33.960 --> 26:35.940
We were shooting "Love On a Sunny Day."

26:36.350 --> 26:38.500
The female lead's stunt double was injured

26:38.530 --> 26:40.300
and we needed a replacement.

26:40.710 --> 26:41.390
So the assistant director

26:41.430 --> 26:42.550
introduced a stuntwoman.

26:42.750 --> 26:43.750
I checked her out

26:43.940 --> 26:45.280
and her skills and basics

26:45.310 --> 26:46.640
were all decent.

26:46.660 --> 26:48.050
So she stayed on.

26:50.570 --> 26:52.490
Was there anyone from the crew

26:52.510 --> 26:53.950
who was close to her

26:54.150 --> 26:55.540
or interacted a lot with her?

26:55.570 --> 26:56.720
Well, Xiao Wei

26:56.780 --> 26:58.260
was very unsociable.

26:58.770 --> 26:59.730
She rarely spoke.

26:59.830 --> 27:01.460
At the set, she just

27:01.710 --> 27:02.370
worked,

27:02.710 --> 27:04.030
got her pay, and left.

27:05.120 --> 27:06.940
Did your boss, Mr. Wen,

27:07.800 --> 27:08.750
interact with

27:08.750 --> 27:09.510
Xiao Wei?

27:09.640 --> 27:10.550
Mr. Wen?

27:12.470 --> 27:13.540
I doubt it.

27:13.830 --> 27:15.120
Investors seldom

27:15.150 --> 27:16.290
come on set.

27:17.190 --> 27:18.760
Right, I remember.

27:19.000 --> 27:19.800
It was when

27:19.830 --> 27:20.740
we were about to wrap.

27:20.790 --> 27:21.510
On set,

27:21.530 --> 27:22.710
Xiao Wei got into a fight with

27:22.750 --> 27:23.570
the assistant director.

27:23.710 --> 27:24.390
I think

27:24.680 --> 27:26.180
Mr. Wen was there that day.

27:27.910 --> 27:28.910
Why did they fight?

27:30.190 --> 27:31.270
I don't know why

27:31.290 --> 27:32.400
specifically.

27:32.820 --> 27:33.820
It was probably...

27:34.750 --> 27:35.840
about money.

27:36.050 --> 27:37.440
Because though Xiao Wei

27:37.590 --> 27:38.480
rarely spoke,

27:38.510 --> 27:40.030
I could sense that

27:40.230 --> 27:41.570
she cared about money.

27:42.220 --> 27:44.240
Since Mr. Wen was there,

27:44.320 --> 27:45.670
how did he handle that?

27:45.860 --> 27:47.750
It was such a big deal.

27:48.030 --> 27:48.640
The assistant director

27:48.670 --> 27:49.900
was seriously injured

27:50.110 --> 27:51.250
and insisted on calling the cops.

27:51.510 --> 27:53.060
Mr. Wen stepped up and suppressed it.

27:53.140 --> 27:54.380
I think Mr. Wen had to

27:54.410 --> 27:55.520
compensate him.

27:56.850 --> 27:57.600
Director.

27:57.830 --> 27:58.760
Don't mind me asking this,

27:59.740 --> 28:00.670
but based on your

28:00.710 --> 28:01.710
understanding of Mr. Wen,

28:02.100 --> 28:03.290
if he spent so much money

28:03.320 --> 28:04.730
to settle something for a girl,

28:05.290 --> 28:06.670
do you think they

28:06.700 --> 28:07.900
could've taken things

28:07.950 --> 28:09.190
a step further or something?

28:11.450 --> 28:12.900
No, I doubt that happened.

28:14.490 --> 28:15.410
I don't think so.

28:15.440 --> 28:16.680
I don't know the details.

28:18.370 --> 28:18.810
Okay.

28:18.830 --> 28:19.620
I'm just kidding.

28:19.650 --> 28:20.400
Sorry for troubling you.

28:20.440 --> 28:20.950
No problem.

28:20.950 --> 28:21.350
Thanks, director.

28:21.410 --> 28:22.440
Sorry for taking your time.

28:22.460 --> 28:23.200
Okay, okay.

28:23.230 --> 28:23.670
Thanks, guys.

28:24.510 --> 28:24.830
Okay, bye.

28:24.830 --> 28:25.350
Bye.

28:30.610 --> 28:33.490
[Police]

28:33.870 --> 28:35.130
If that's the case,

28:35.480 --> 28:36.550
we can link

28:36.850 --> 28:38.350
all of them with Wen Peng.

28:38.750 --> 28:39.470
Deng Man,

28:40.150 --> 28:41.250
Yu Bofeng,

28:41.790 --> 28:44.000
Zhou Zhicheng, Ding Jing, Wang Qianqian,

28:44.510 --> 28:45.270
and even Jiang,

28:45.290 --> 28:46.040
you too.

28:46.640 --> 28:47.900
As long as Wen Peng's involved,

28:47.920 --> 28:49.250
everyone can be linked together.

28:50.920 --> 28:52.690
But with every incident,

28:52.880 --> 28:54.100
Wen Peng had

28:54.150 --> 28:55.030
a verified alibi.

28:55.320 --> 28:57.140
We haven't figured out his motive either.

28:57.340 --> 28:58.860
So we can't summon him now.

28:59.490 --> 29:00.180
Yes.

29:01.000 --> 29:02.160
Wen Peng has always kept

29:02.190 --> 29:03.470
his own hands clean.

29:03.690 --> 29:04.550
He also has verified

29:04.630 --> 29:05.430
alibis.

29:06.410 --> 29:08.060
So the question now is

29:08.700 --> 29:11.170
that if Li Ruonan is his hands,

29:11.250 --> 29:12.780
how's he controlling her?

29:15.040 --> 29:16.360
With Li Ruonan's mother.

29:20.000 --> 29:21.030
Any news from

29:21.110 --> 29:21.760
Chengzhou?

29:21.780 --> 29:23.240
Bits and pieces were sent back,

29:23.350 --> 29:24.510
but they're all worthless.

29:24.700 --> 29:25.780
Nothing about the whereabouts

29:25.810 --> 29:27.230
of Li Ruonan's mother.

29:30.500 --> 29:31.970
They're too slow.

29:32.800 --> 29:34.150
How about I go there?

29:36.410 --> 29:37.070
Sure.

29:38.350 --> 29:38.980
Liu Hao.

29:39.450 --> 29:40.120
Yes.

29:40.280 --> 29:41.610
Go with Professor Yu.

29:42.190 --> 29:43.200
At Chengzhou,

29:43.410 --> 29:45.280
figure out everything about

29:45.500 --> 29:46.480
Li Ruonan

29:46.500 --> 29:48.100
and the whereabouts

29:48.290 --> 29:49.560
of her mother.

29:49.870 --> 29:50.570
Got it.

29:50.990 --> 29:51.470
Qin Yue.

29:51.760 --> 29:52.380
Yes.

29:52.720 --> 29:53.570
Go to

29:53.590 --> 29:54.880
the Household Department

29:55.480 --> 29:57.550
and send me all of Wen Peng's

29:58.500 --> 29:59.370
information.

29:59.390 --> 30:00.580
Okay. I’ll go now.

30:09.100 --> 30:09.990
Mr. Wen.

30:10.160 --> 30:11.450
This is the real-time report

30:11.470 --> 30:12.990
of our film crews' shoots.

30:13.690 --> 30:14.910
Anything wrong?

30:15.650 --> 30:16.810
It's going well.

30:17.280 --> 30:19.720
But two policemen showed up at the shoot

30:19.780 --> 30:21.020
in Hengdian yesterday.

30:23.160 --> 30:24.090
Police?

30:25.600 --> 30:26.720
What was it for?

30:27.000 --> 30:28.920
I think they were looking for Liu Lin,

30:28.940 --> 30:30.000
our martial arts director.

30:33.760 --> 30:34.870
Okay, noted.

30:44.210 --> 30:46.580
[Anshan Criminal Investigation]

30:45.830 --> 30:47.380
At Chengzhou,

30:47.540 --> 30:48.520
be careful.

30:49.340 --> 30:50.500
If there's anything,

30:50.660 --> 30:51.470
contact me.

30:51.500 --> 30:51.990
Okay.

30:51.990 --> 30:52.800
I have a classmate there.

30:52.830 --> 30:53.580
Don't worry.

30:54.480 --> 30:55.740
How's it going with

30:55.930 --> 30:56.610
Yu Bofeng?

30:59.050 --> 31:00.620
We haven't been in touch.

31:01.280 --> 31:02.650
I think...

31:04.500 --> 31:06.050
we'll never see each other again.

31:07.270 --> 31:08.420
Don't be so pessimistic.

31:08.510 --> 31:10.360
When you come back, find a chance

31:10.790 --> 31:11.470
to talk to him.

31:13.550 --> 31:14.610
We'll see.

31:14.780 --> 31:15.780
Bye.

31:15.340 --> 31:17.060
[Defending justice, forging the spirit of the police]

31:18.500 --> 31:19.210
Hello, psychologist.

31:19.230 --> 31:19.840
Bye.

31:20.320 --> 31:20.980
Jiang.

31:21.090 --> 31:22.330
The info you asked for.

31:22.330 --> 31:25.820
[Office of Criminal Investigation Unit]

31:22.380 --> 31:23.210
Wen Peng's info.

31:23.710 --> 31:24.550
He's from Longhai.

31:24.570 --> 31:25.870
He came to Ninghai to attend

31:25.900 --> 31:27.080
Ninghai University.

31:27.870 --> 31:29.320
He went abroad in 2015.

31:28.880 --> 31:31.210
[Personal Information]

31:29.340 --> 31:30.950
His university was a five-year course.

31:30.970 --> 31:31.790
He went abroad before

31:31.830 --> 31:32.310
graduating.

31:32.350 --> 31:33.090
It's marked as a drop-out.

31:33.120 --> 31:34.630
His family is very simple.

31:34.650 --> 31:35.790
His parents divorced early,

31:34.740 --> 31:39.350
[Main social relationships]

31:36.190 --> 31:38.120
and he lived with his father.

31:38.150 --> 31:39.400
His father didn't remarry,

31:39.430 --> 31:40.620
so he doesn't have siblings.

31:42.840 --> 31:44.520
[Main Social Relationships] [Mother: He Yan]

31:46.480 --> 31:47.690
W-What's wrong, Jiang?

31:52.690 --> 31:54.440
[Defending justice, forging the spirit of the police]

31:55.690 --> 31:56.960
What's wrong, Jiang?

31:59.140 --> 31:59.840
Jiang.

32:01.840 --> 32:02.590
Jiang!

32:06.890 --> 32:07.670
Isn't the color

32:07.690 --> 32:09.180
a bit old-fashioned?

32:09.210 --> 32:10.840
You don't understand.

32:11.150 --> 32:12.710
The receptionist told me

32:12.740 --> 32:14.100
this is the trendiest color,

32:14.130 --> 32:16.640
called the Maillard.

32:16.920 --> 32:18.830
And you just took her word for it?

32:18.960 --> 32:19.400
Of course.

32:19.430 --> 32:20.570
Young ladies like this stuff,

32:20.640 --> 32:21.270
-you know?
-Is it?

32:21.290 --> 32:22.120
Look at this too.

32:23.300 --> 32:24.610
I'll let you touch it.

32:25.550 --> 32:26.200
Okay, enough.

32:26.230 --> 32:26.940
Don't dirty it.

32:26.960 --> 32:28.130
The texture's really great.

32:28.150 --> 32:28.720
It's real silk.

32:28.750 --> 32:30.110
Let's buy one for ourselves.

32:30.420 --> 32:31.060
It's over 10,000 yuan.

32:31.400 --> 32:31.930
Forget it.

32:31.960 --> 32:32.940
I don't want it. No thanks.

32:34.920 --> 32:36.010
You know what?

32:36.030 --> 32:37.520
If our son really

32:37.550 --> 32:39.390
manages to marry Yan,

32:40.040 --> 32:41.380
I'll smile even in my sleep.

32:41.400 --> 32:42.910
They'll definitely get married.

32:42.930 --> 32:44.110
The key is to give us a grandchild

32:44.190 --> 32:44.830
as soon as possible.

32:44.860 --> 32:45.360
Yes!

32:45.390 --> 32:45.990
Right?

32:46.010 --> 32:47.490
But we can't rush about that.

32:47.510 --> 32:48.730
Don't pressure them!

32:48.790 --> 32:49.150
Dad!

32:49.150 --> 32:49.860
I want a grandchild.

32:49.880 --> 32:50.620
Mom!

32:50.650 --> 32:51.220
Look.

32:51.240 --> 32:51.670
Speak of the devil.

32:51.670 --> 32:52.330
You're back!

32:52.430 --> 32:53.090
I know.

32:53.150 --> 32:53.940
What are you doing?

32:54.370 --> 32:55.730
Come and take a look.

32:55.960 --> 32:57.440
It's the gift I picked for Yan.

32:57.470 --> 32:58.080
Don't you

32:58.250 --> 32:59.510
have work today?

33:00.260 --> 33:01.020
I do.

33:01.040 --> 33:01.670
I'm just visiting.

33:01.700 --> 33:02.600
I bought it for Yan.

33:02.630 --> 33:03.540
Will she like it?

33:03.560 --> 33:05.040
It's from you. Of course she will.

33:05.070 --> 33:05.840
See?

33:07.670 --> 33:08.420
Um...

33:10.570 --> 33:11.570
Um...

33:12.260 --> 33:13.110
Have something to say?

33:13.910 --> 33:14.480
Yes.

33:15.380 --> 33:17.000
When I was looking through records

33:17.790 --> 33:19.300
in the office today...

33:20.690 --> 33:22.030
I'll get to the point, Mom.

33:23.150 --> 33:24.310
-Well…
-What's wrong?

33:25.040 --> 33:25.630
Mom.

33:26.660 --> 33:28.040
Wen Peng's your son, right?

33:34.510 --> 33:35.240
I...

33:39.870 --> 33:40.670
Yes.

33:45.760 --> 33:46.600
Mom!

33:49.280 --> 33:50.050
Mom.

33:53.970 --> 33:55.060
School is over?

33:55.780 --> 33:57.180
Did you have fun today?

33:57.880 --> 33:58.650
Mom.

33:58.680 --> 34:00.090
Did he hit you again?

34:02.580 --> 34:03.630
No.

34:04.710 --> 34:06.300
I fell down.

34:07.030 --> 34:08.030
Does it hurt?

34:12.110 --> 34:12.960
Don't worry.

34:15.020 --> 34:16.010
It doesn't hurt.

34:16.630 --> 34:18.739
I really fell down.

34:20.920 --> 34:21.639
Mom.

34:22.060 --> 34:22.820
Just leave.

34:24.260 --> 34:25.420
Don't come back.

34:27.219 --> 34:28.639
If I stall my dad...

34:31.310 --> 34:33.110
you won't be beaten by him again.

34:35.800 --> 34:37.090
My son's all grown up.

34:43.130 --> 34:44.610
My son's all grown up.

34:50.969 --> 34:52.030
I promise you.

34:55.159 --> 34:56.659
After I settle down,

34:58.400 --> 34:59.960
I’ll come pick you up.

35:15.100 --> 35:15.850
Mr. Wen.

35:16.240 --> 35:17.070
You asked for me?

35:17.790 --> 35:19.020
Contact the police station.

35:19.410 --> 35:20.790
Tell them I want to see Yu Bofeng.

35:21.320 --> 35:22.000
Yes.

35:31.510 --> 35:32.430
Did you say...

35:35.360 --> 35:37.340
he has been in Ninghai all this time?

35:39.310 --> 35:39.820
Yes.

35:43.690 --> 35:45.080
Impossible.

35:45.140 --> 35:46.740
Did you find the wrong person

35:46.780 --> 35:47.790
with the same name?

35:47.830 --> 35:48.540
He was

35:48.560 --> 35:51.030
sent abroad by his dad when he was young.

35:51.060 --> 35:52.710
His aunt has been updating me

35:52.790 --> 35:53.740
about that kid,

35:53.760 --> 35:54.440
you know?

35:54.470 --> 35:55.130
Look!

35:55.380 --> 35:56.710
I've always been

35:56.740 --> 35:58.490
texting him during festivals.

35:58.520 --> 35:59.440
Look!

36:02.440 --> 36:03.410
Mom.

36:04.190 --> 36:05.840
There are photos on the file.

36:06.150 --> 36:06.790
It can't be wrong.

36:14.880 --> 36:16.560
He has been in Ninghai all these years.

36:16.580 --> 36:18.490
He was even my university classmate.

36:19.130 --> 36:20.280
Both he and Lu Yan

36:20.310 --> 36:21.310
majored in medicine.

36:22.740 --> 36:23.790
He studied abroad,

36:23.820 --> 36:25.280
but he came back soon after.

36:27.890 --> 36:29.190
He's always been in Ninghai?

36:35.750 --> 36:36.350
Al...

36:38.240 --> 36:39.350
Always?

36:41.320 --> 36:42.370
Chengyi.

36:43.220 --> 36:44.780
Can you take me to him?

36:46.230 --> 36:47.850
T-Take me to him.

36:47.920 --> 36:48.400
No, no.

36:48.430 --> 36:49.210
I don't believe it.

36:49.270 --> 36:50.800
They've been lying to me!

36:50.910 --> 36:51.560
I've been looking

36:51.590 --> 36:52.540
for him for years!

36:52.570 --> 36:53.640
Now you tell me...

36:53.840 --> 36:55.130
Calm down. Calm down.

36:55.370 --> 36:56.060
Don't...

36:57.040 --> 36:57.840
Why?

36:57.950 --> 36:58.710
Calm down.

36:58.730 --> 36:59.510
Why?

37:17.900 --> 37:18.460
Chengyi.

37:19.860 --> 37:20.840
Is Wen Peng

37:21.390 --> 37:22.750
related to the case you're

37:22.750 --> 37:23.430
investigating?

37:26.710 --> 37:27.720
A probable suspect.

37:30.860 --> 37:31.830
Is it because you're

37:31.870 --> 37:33.070
worried about your mom,

37:33.210 --> 37:34.200
so you...

37:36.570 --> 37:37.600
I wanted to see

37:37.630 --> 37:39.550
whether she could accept it.

37:39.580 --> 37:41.320
I wanted to see her reaction.

37:42.270 --> 37:43.540
But I ended up...

37:44.620 --> 37:45.520
Remember,

37:46.930 --> 37:47.930
you're a police officer.

37:49.120 --> 37:50.450
Do what you should do.

37:51.080 --> 37:52.580
Your mom will understand.

38:10.590 --> 38:12.480
You shouldn't have come, Wen.

38:16.870 --> 38:18.070
I don't want you to

38:18.070 --> 38:18.910
see me like this.

38:21.680 --> 38:22.960
Because of my incompetence,

38:23.600 --> 38:24.750
you're suffering.

38:25.290 --> 38:26.320
Don't say that.

38:28.930 --> 38:29.990
You've done more than

38:30.010 --> 38:30.890
enough for me.

38:34.100 --> 38:35.500
I’ve always wanted to

38:35.540 --> 38:37.050
reconcile this with Jiang Chengyi.

38:37.360 --> 38:38.180
But he

38:38.210 --> 38:39.990
really wouldn't yield.

38:42.760 --> 38:43.520
Originally,

38:43.730 --> 38:44.420
this matter

38:44.440 --> 38:45.550
isn't that serious.

38:45.580 --> 38:47.310
As long as he forgives you,

38:47.330 --> 38:48.730
it'll blow over.

38:48.750 --> 38:49.520
But he...

38:49.540 --> 38:50.950
I don't want his forgiveness.

38:52.700 --> 38:54.320
Let him destroy me.

38:55.700 --> 38:56.510
It's not his

38:56.550 --> 38:57.510
first time anyway.

39:02.330 --> 39:03.020
How about this?

39:03.830 --> 39:04.810
For the next few days,

39:04.840 --> 39:06.520
Be good while you're inside

39:06.600 --> 39:08.310
and calm yourself down.

39:08.550 --> 39:10.180
We'll talk after you get out.

39:13.810 --> 39:15.070
Wait for me, Wen.

39:16.400 --> 39:17.280
I'll wait for you.

39:18.530 --> 39:20.000
But I promise this matter

39:20.030 --> 39:21.810
won't just end like this.

39:37.400 --> 39:38.250
You're back.

39:38.430 --> 39:39.250
Yes, I'm back.

39:47.590 --> 39:48.420
What's wrong?

39:48.450 --> 39:50.360
Why are you sighing so much?

39:52.970 --> 39:54.400
I discovered something,

39:54.650 --> 39:56.150
but I don't know how to talk about it.

39:58.120 --> 39:58.970
What is it?

40:03.270 --> 40:04.840
Wen Peng's...

40:06.430 --> 40:07.950
biological mother

40:09.830 --> 40:10.880
is my mother.

40:16.240 --> 40:17.600
Are you kidding?

40:17.900 --> 40:18.340
It's true.

40:25.610 --> 40:26.370
All these years,

40:26.400 --> 40:27.630
Wen Peng hasn't contacted her.

40:30.090 --> 40:31.530
She couldn't find Wen Peng either.

40:32.250 --> 40:33.230
But Wen Peng was in

40:33.270 --> 40:34.030
the same university

40:34.430 --> 40:35.430
and basketball team as me.

40:37.430 --> 40:39.170
No wonder he was

40:39.700 --> 40:40.790
always so

40:40.790 --> 40:41.870
hostile to me.

41:14.590 --> 41:15.620
[Leading the new trend of civilization and creating a civilized campus]

41:15.740 --> 41:18.660
[Jiang Chengyi: Merit Student]

41:22.310 --> 41:25.960
[Jiang wants to be a police officer.]

41:25.960 --> 41:26.620
[Ninghai Uni, I'm coming!]

41:28.990 --> 41:31.900
[Welcome, new talents! Let's work together to create a better future!]

41:34.280 --> 41:36.310
[List of Freshmen]

41:38.460 --> 41:41.610
[Jiang Chengyi, Male, Department of Safety Engineering]

41:44.610 --> 41:48.250
[Wen Peng, Male, Department of Medicine]

41:57.630 --> 41:58.670
Faster! Faster!

41:58.700 --> 41:59.500
All of you!

42:02.190 --> 42:02.870
Hello, Coach.

42:03.650 --> 42:05.310
I want to join the basketball team.

42:06.330 --> 42:06.940
Kid.

42:06.970 --> 42:08.010
This is the school team.

42:08.030 --> 42:09.850
You need to pass the tryouts.

42:10.510 --> 42:11.550
If you want to play,

42:11.630 --> 42:12.960
you can join your department team first.

42:14.480 --> 42:16.900
Do they play in the department competition too?

42:16.940 --> 42:17.630
Yes.

42:19.120 --> 42:20.280
The one in the black vest

42:20.650 --> 42:21.850
is Jiang Chengyi.

42:22.020 --> 42:23.660
He’s the captain of the Engineering team.

42:23.750 --> 42:24.840
If you want to play,

42:24.860 --> 42:26.210
you can ask your department's captain.

42:29.610 --> 42:30.390
Thank you, Coach.

42:39.590 --> 42:40.140
What a coincidence,

42:40.350 --> 42:40.950
really.

42:41.720 --> 42:42.340
He...

42:43.590 --> 42:46.040
He was always so hostile to you because

42:47.160 --> 42:48.310
he transferred

42:48.350 --> 42:49.590
his hatred onto you?

42:52.700 --> 42:54.010
Like you said,

42:54.030 --> 42:57.340
his dad beat him up as a kid

42:58.390 --> 43:00.420
and his mother abandoned him,

43:01.490 --> 43:02.720
so he might hate me.

43:04.160 --> 43:04.970
But what does this

43:05.030 --> 43:05.910
have to do with me?

43:09.230 --> 43:10.930
I was abandoned by my own mother too.

43:12.460 --> 43:13.670
No, it's...

43:18.280 --> 43:19.500
So...

43:20.190 --> 43:22.130
I was wondering why

43:22.310 --> 43:23.900
you asked me about Wen Peng.

43:24.190 --> 43:25.410
Are you investigating him?

43:26.750 --> 43:28.370
I've been investigating something,

43:29.440 --> 43:30.610
and I think something's off

43:32.060 --> 43:32.710
with Wen Peng.
